name: Litejokes

overview:
In the fast life of today, people have forgotten how to smile. Litejokes provides people short and funny jokes. These jokes are provided free on their website http://www.litejokes.com and on their facebook page http://www.facebook.com/mylitejokes . This company has also release three jokes books: in English, Hindi and Punjabi languages each.

They also send fun stuff in email to more than 29,000 subscribers on their google group. This group can be found at: www.groups.google.com/group/litejokes

There are numerous jokes websites, but I like this website because they only provide short jokes, not long stories. People have no time in reading long stories.
